Discover iDapps and Tools

This section provides an overview of the different iDapps developed using Router's infrastructure. Additionally, you can access essential tools required for interacting with Router's infrastructure.

iDapps​

Ping Pong
A iDapp using which you can transfer message from one chain to another.
Voyager
An asset transfer dApp built using Router's omnichain framework providing seamless cross-chain swaps.
Texchange
An iDapp to exchange testnet tokens.

Tools​

Router Explorer
A block explorer to monitor cross-chain transactions.
Router Station
A tool to manage contract lifecycle-related processes on the Router chain.
Router Faucet
A tool to get testnet tokens for performing tasks on Testnet.
Router Hub
An tool for delegating ROUTE tokens to validators.
Router Sandbox
An easy-to-use prototyping environment for interoperable dApps built using Router.
